parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose braking ability, leading to accidents, fires, or near-misses, which can result in serious injuries or fatalities.

symptoms: The ABS brake sensors burn up
causing the front brakes to lock up
